      "id": "sybil_8_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a total showstopper? I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute dream of a car, and honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one\u2014not a single scratch or dent to be found. It drives like an absolute dream and the interior still has that fresh feel. I\u2019ve truly loved and cared for this beauty, and I\u2019m looking for someone who will enjoy it just as much as I have. You\u2019ve gotta see it to believe how pristine it is!",
