    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine, collector-grade condition. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, utilizing six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double-VANOS for optimized volumetric efficiency across the power band. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec M-Variable limited-slip differential. Crucially, this vehicle has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement. The suspension geometry remains perfectly true, and the exterior exhibits factory-fresh paint depth with no evidence of panel gap misalignment. A mechanically flawless example for the serious enthusiast.",
