    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that defies its age. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in a factory-fresh appearance. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely zero rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the premium leather upholstery remains supple and free of any creasing or bolster wear, still carrying that distinct new-car aroma. Every button, switch, and electronic component functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach; the engine runs with whisper-quiet precision, and the transmission shifts are imperceptible. We have a complete binder of service records from day one, documenting every oil change and inspection performed by certified technicians. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade example for the most discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
